@startuml
actor Customer
participant Frontend
participant "DRF API" as API
database PostgreSQL

Customer -> Frontend: Click "Add to cart"
Frontend -> API: POST /api/carts/{id}/items
API -> PostgreSQL: Insert/Update CartItem
PostgreSQL --> API: Saved
API --> Frontend: Updated cart
Customer -> Frontend: Open cart page
Frontend -> API: GET /api/carts/{id}
API -> PostgreSQL: Fetch cart + items
API --> Frontend: Cart JSON
Frontend --> Customer: Show total + quantity
@enduml
